          = image_tag "icon/icon-01.png", height: "337.61", width: "219.33"
        %h3.item__subtitle 簡単に売り買いできる
        %p.item__detail
          スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
      %section.item
        %figure.item__img
          = image_tag "icon/icon-03.png", height: "337.61", width: "219.33"
